14424685649922|title=#Buccaneers and DT Rakeem Nunzez-Roches agreed to 1-year deal for up to $2.25m ($1m gtd), source said. Could see more time with Beau Allen signing with Pats.|last=Caplan|first=Adam|website=twitter.com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n|1 year, $2.25M<ref name=\":7\" />\n|-style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Defensive end|DE]]\n|[[Ndamukong Suh]]\n|Tampa Bay Buccaneers\n|March 26, 2020<ref name=\":8\">{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/RapSheet/status/1242876632458821632|title=#Bucs DL Ndamukong Suh is expected to re-sign on a 1-year deal worth $8M, sources tell me and @MikeGarafolo. He wanted to return to play for DC Todd Bowles, and it should be done soon|last=Rapoport|first=Ian|website=twitter.com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|1 year, $8M<ref name=\":8\" />\n|-\n|[[Linebacker|OLB]]\n|[[Sam Acho]]\n|\n|\n|\n|-style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Linebacker|OLB]]\n|[[Shaquil Barrett]]\n|Tampa Bay Buccaneers\n|March 16, 2020<ref name=\":9\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bucsnation.com/2020/3/16/21180488/buccaneers-place-franchise-tag-on-shaquil-barrett-2020|title=Buccaneers place franchise tag on Shaquil Barrett|last=Yarcho|first=James|date=2020-03-16|website=www.bucsnation.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref>\n|Franchise tagged for 1 year, $15.8 million<ref name=\":9\" />\n|-style=\"background:#cfc\"\n|[[Linebacker|ILB]]\n|[[Kevin Minter]]\n|Tampa Bay Buccaneers\n|March 20, 2020<ref name=\":10\">{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/AaronWilson_NFL/status/1241105988888997896|title=Kevin Minter (Buccaneers), $1.187 million one-year deal, $137,500 roster bonus 3rd day after contract execution, $1.05M base salary, veteran minimum salary benefit|last=Wilson|first=Aaron|website=twitter|language=en|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>\n|1 year. $1.18M<ref name=\":10\" />\n|-style=\"background:#fcc\"\n|[[Linebacker|OLB]]\n|[[Carl Nassib]]\n|[[2020 Las Vegas Raiders season|Las Vegas Raiders]]\n|March 17, 2020<ref name=\":11\">{{Cite web|url