ications.com/Pages/2020-Opponents-Determined.aspx |work=NFL Communications |date=December 30, 2019 |accessdate=December 30, 2019}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers|year=2020|border=2}}\"| Category !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Home !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Away\n|-\n| '''Division opponents'''<br>([[NFC South]]) || colspan=2| [[2020 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta Falcons]]<br>[[2020 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]<br>[[2020 New Orleans Saints season|New Orleans Saints]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>([[NFC North]]) || [[2020 Green Bay Packers season|Green Bay Packers]]<br>[[2020 Minnesota Vikings season|Minnesota Vikings]] || [[2020 Chicago Bears season|Chicago Bears]]<br>[[2020 Detroit Lions season|Detroit Lions]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>(based on {{nfly|2019}} division placement) || [[2020 Los Angeles Rams season|Los Angeles Rams]] || [[2020 New York Giants season|New York Giants]]\n|-\n| '''Interconference opponents'''<br>([[AFC West]]) || [[2020 Kansas City Chiefs season|Kansas City Chiefs]]<br>[[2020 Los Angeles Chargers season|Los Angeles Chargers]] || [[2020 Denver Broncos season|Denver Broncos]]<br>[[2020 Las Vegas Raiders season|Las Vegas Raiders]]\n|}\n<!--\n===Game summaries===\n====Week #: vs. Atlanta Falcons====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Tampa Bay Buccaneers|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Atlanta Falcons at Tampa Bay Buccaneers&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Falcons\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Buccaneers\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=Raymond James Stadium, Tampa, Florida\n|attendance=\n|weather=\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: vs. Carolina Panthers====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlesty